				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The Hag is about to perform her eye-extraction and replanting on you. She is in her hag form in all its disgusting glory. Initially she's happy and feeling powerful -- but when she finds out your tadpole is Netherese, she becomes angry; not quite frightened, but anxious about having that magic in her home. She wants you out and has no more patience for you."
				}
